window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Wide open spaces. Ancient ruins. Pissed off governments. Five adventurous students. </b> </p> <p>What could possibly go wrong? </p> <p>Tag along as we follow Alpha Class as they study with Jeo, the lead of the Engineering team, and learn about engineering by reviewing important marvels across the earth. </p> <p>Without getting permission. </p> <p><b>If they thought the moon was dangerous, wait till they return to Earth.</b> </p> <p>A Kurtherian Gambit Adventure for younger listeners...or those who are young at heart.</p>"; 
